<p>
  <span class="nym">Ignatius</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>Ignatius</i>, the name of a Roman <i>gens</i>, sometimes connected with <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>ignis</i> 'fiery'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 1st-2nd C saint and a 9th C Byzantine saint.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


