 <span class="name">Ignatha</span> (<span class="case">nom</span>) <a href="../cite/Ignatha/1582/Audén1980"><span class="bib_key">ibid.</span> <span class="bib_loc">p. 171</span></a></dd>
</dl>
</dd>
